## What is MercadoMi? ‚úÖ ADICIONADO (parcialmente - conte√∫do est√° no FAQ)

MercadoMi is a comprehensive home improvement platform that connects homeowners with verified professionals for renovation, repair, and maintenance services. Our app streamlines the entire process‚Äîfrom finding the right professional to managing your project timeline and payments‚Äîgiving you complete control and peace of mind.

**Key Features:**
- **Verified Professionals**: All service providers are vetted and verified ‚úÖ (mencionado nos Benefits)
- **Expert Consultations**: Get professional advice before starting your project ‚úÖ (mencionado nos Benefits)
- **Smart Material Search**: Find and compare products from major retailers ‚úÖ (mencionado nos Benefits)
- **Project Management**: Track progress with milestone-based timelines ‚úÖ (mencionado nos Benefits)
- **Secure Payments**: Protected escrow system ensures your money is safe ‚úÖ (mencionado nos Benefits)
- **Real-time Communication**: Chat directly with professionals throughout your project ‚úÖ (mencionado nos Benefits)

