### 2. **Get Expert Consultations** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO (como bullet)
Not sure where to start? Our consultant service provides professional guidance to help you plan your project, understand costs, and make informed decisions before committing to a full renovation.

### 3. **Smart Home Scanning Technology** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO (como bullet)
Use our integrated CubiCasa technology to create accurate floor plans of your home. Simply take photos or videos, and receive professional floor plans with measurements‚Äîperfect for planning renovations and getting accurate quotes.

### 4. **Compare Products and Prices** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO (como bullet)
Search for materials and products from major retailers like Home Depot and Lowe's directly within the app. Compare prices, read reviews, and add items to your project quote‚Äîall in one place.

### 5. **Milestone-Based Project Management** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO (como bullet)
Break down your project into manageable milestones. Track progress in real-time, approve completed stages, and ensure quality work at every step. You're always in control.

### 6. **Secure Payment Protection** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO (se√ß√£o principal)
Your payments are held in escrow until milestones are completed and approved. This ensures professionals are paid fairly while protecting you from incomplete or unsatisfactory work.

### 7. **Real-time Communication** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO (como bullet)
Chat directly with professionals and consultants throughout your project. Share photos, ask questions, and stay updated on progress‚Äîall within the app.

### 8. **Complete Project Transparency** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO (como bullet)
View detailed quotes, material lists, timelines, and progress updates. Everything is documented, so you always know what's happening with your project.

### 9. **Team Collaboration** ‚ùå N√ÉO ADICIONADO (n√£o h√° se√ß√£o espec√≠fica)
