## How It Works ‚ùå N√ÉO ADICIONADO (n√£o h√° se√ß√£o espec√≠fica para isso)

### Step 1: **Create Your Service Request**
Describe your home improvement needs, select a service category, and add photos or use our home scanning feature to create accurate floor plans.

### Step 2: **Get Professional Quotes**
Receive detailed quotes from verified professionals in your area. Compare prices, timelines, and approaches to find the best fit for your project.

### Step 3: **Optional: Consult with an Expert**
If you need guidance, book a consultation with one of our expert consultants. Get professional advice on design, materials, and project planning.

### Step 4: **Select Materials**
Browse and select materials from major retailers. Add products directly to your project quote for accurate cost estimation.

### Step 5: **Approve & Fund Your Project**
Review the final quote, approve milestones, and securely fund your project through our escrow system. Your payment is protected until work is completed.

### Step 6: **Track Progress**
Monitor your project through milestone-based timelines. Approve completed stages, communicate with your professional, and watch your home transformation happen.

### Step 7: **Complete & Review**
Once all milestones are completed and approved, release final payment and leave a review to help other homeowners make informed decisions.

