## Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) ‚úÖ ADICIONADO (6 perguntas essenciais)

### ‚úÖ **What is MercadoMi?** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO
MercadoMi is a comprehensive home improvement platform that connects homeowners with verified professionals for renovation, repair, and maintenance services. We provide tools for project management, material sourcing, and secure payments.

### ‚úÖ **How do I find a professional?** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO
Simply create a service request describing your needs. Verified professionals in your area will send you detailed quotes. You can browse their profiles, ratings, and portfolios before making a decision.

### ‚ùå **What is the consultant service?** ‚ùå REMOVIDO (pode ser mencionado nos Benefits)
Our consultant service provides expert guidance for your home improvement projects. Consultants help you plan your project, understand costs, choose materials, and make informed decisions‚Äîperfect if you're unsure where to start.

### ‚úÖ **How does the payment system work?** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO
We use an escrow system to protect both you and the professional. Your payment is held securely until project milestones are completed and approved. This ensures quality work while protecting your investment.

### ‚úÖ **What are milestones?** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO
Milestones break your project into manageable stages. Each milestone has a specific scope, timeline, and payment amount. You approve each stage before the professional moves to the next, ensuring quality and transparency.

### ‚ùå **Can I purchase materials through the app?** ‚ùå REMOVIDO (mencionado nos Benefits)
Yes! You can search for materials and products from major retailers like Home Depot and Lowe's. Compare prices, read reviews, and add items to your project quote.

### ‚ùå **What is the home scanning feature?** ‚ùå REMOVIDO (mencionado nos Benefits)
Our integrated CubiCasa technology allows you to create accurate floor plans by taking photos or videos of your home. This helps professionals provide more accurate quotes and better project planning.

### ‚úÖ **Is my payment information secure?** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO
Absolutely. We use industry-standard encryption and secure payment processing through Stripe. Your payment information is never stored on our servers.

### ‚ùå **What if I'm not satisfied with the work?** ‚ùå REMOVIDO (coberto pela pergunta de milestones)
Our milestone approval system allows you to request changes before approving each stage. If issues arise, you can communicate directly with the professional or contact our support team for assistance.

### ‚ùå **Can professionals work in teams?** ‚ùå REMOVIDO (menos essencial)
Yes, for larger projects, professionals can invite team members. You'll see the entire team and can communicate with everyone involved in your project.

### ‚ùå **How do I track my project progress?** ‚ùå REMOVIDO (mencionado nos Benefits)
The app provides a real-time timeline showing all milestones, their status, and progress updates. You'll receive notifications for important updates and can chat with professionals at any time.

### ‚ùå **Are there any fees for using MercadoMi?** ‚ùå REMOVIDO (menos essencial)
Creating service requests and browsing professionals is free. Fees may apply for certain premium features or services. All costs are clearly displayed before you commit.

### ‚ùå **What areas do you serve?** ‚ùå REMOVIDO (menos essencial)
MercadoMi is available in multiple regions. Check the app to see professionals available in your area.

### ‚úÖ **How do I get started?** ‚úÖ ADICIONADO
Download the app, create an account, and start by creating your first service request. It's that simple!

