# Mercado Me - Client Journey: Simple Steps

## Overview
This document outlines the simple, secure steps a client takes from creating a service request to having their project completed.

---

## **STEP 1: Create Your Service Request** üìù

**What the client does:**
- Opens the app and taps "Create Service Request"
- Fills in basic information:
  - Service name (e.g., "Kitchen Renovation")
  - Description of what they need
  - Service address
  - Photos of the area (optional but recommended)
- Chooses between:
  - **Open Request**: Any verified professional can see and respond
  - **Direct Request**: Send to a specific professional they've chosen

**Optional but helpful:**
- Use CubiCasa home scanning to create accurate floor plans
- Select a service category (Cleaning, Plumbing, Painting, etc.)

**Security & Ease:**
- ‚úÖ Simple form - takes just a few minutes
- ‚úÖ All information is private and secure
- ‚úÖ Can save as draft and finish later

**What happens next:**
- Request is published and visible to professionals
- Client receives confirmation notification

---

## **STEP 2: Receive Professional Quotes** üíº

**What the client does:**
- Waits for professionals to review their request
- Receives notifications when quotes arrive
- Views all quotes in "My Projects" section

**What professionals send:**
- Detailed quote with:
  - Total price (materials + labor)
  - Estimated timeline
  - List of materials needed
  - Project milestones (if applicable)
  - Professional's notes and approach

**Security & Ease:**
- ‚úÖ All professionals are verified
- ‚úÖ Compare multiple quotes side-by-side
- ‚úÖ See professional ratings and reviews
- ‚úÖ Chat with professionals to ask questions
- ‚úÖ No obligation to accept any quote

**What happens next:**
- Client reviews and compares quotes
- Can request more information or negotiate

---

## **STEP 3: Choose Your Professional** ‚úÖ

**What the client does:**
- Reviews all received quotes
- Compares prices, timelines, and approaches
- Checks professional profiles, ratings, and portfolios
- Chats with professionals if needed
- Selects the best quote for their needs
- Taps "Accept Quote"

**Security & Ease:**
- ‚úÖ See all quote details before deciding
- ‚úÖ Professional profiles with verified credentials
- ‚úÖ Read reviews from other clients
- ‚úÖ Easy comparison tool
- ‚úÖ Can reject quotes without explanation

**What happens next:**
- Selected professional is notified
- Other quotes are automatically declined
- Project status changes to "Accepted - Payment Required"

---

## **STEP 4: Secure Payment** üí≥

**What the client does:**
- Reviews the final accepted quote one more time
- Sees the payment breakdown:
  - Materials cost
  - Labor cost
  - Total amount
- Adds payment method (credit/debit card)
- Makes secure payment through escrow system

**How Escrow Works:**
- Payment is held securely by Mercado Me
- Money is NOT released to professional yet
- Payment is protected until work is completed
- Client approves each milestone before payment is released

**Security & Ease:**
- ‚úÖ Payment is 100% secure (Stripe encryption)
- ‚úÖ Money protected until work is done
- ‚úÖ No payment until you approve milestones
- ‚úÖ Can dispute if work doesn't meet standards
- ‚úÖ Automatic refund protection

**What happens next:**
- Payment is confirmed and held in escrow
- Project status changes to "In Progress"
- Professional can begin work
- First milestone is activated

---

## **STEP 5: Project Execution** üèóÔ∏è

**What the client does:**
- Monitors project progress through milestone timeline
- Receives notifications for each milestone update
- Reviews work completed at each stage
- Approves milestones when satisfied
- Communicates with professional via in-app chat
- Can request changes if needed

**Milestone System:**
- Project is broken into stages (milestones)
- Each milestone has specific work to be completed
- Client must approve each milestone
- Payment for each milestone is released upon approval
- Professional can't move to next milestone without approval

**Security & Ease:**
- ‚úÖ See exactly what's being done at each stage
- ‚úÖ Approve work before paying for it
- ‚úÖ Real-time progress tracking
- ‚úÖ Photo evidence of completed work
- ‚úÖ Direct communication with professional
- ‚úÖ Request changes anytime

**What happens next:**
- Professional completes milestones one by one
- Client approves each milestone
- Payments are released incrementally
- Project moves toward completion

---

## **STEP 6: Project Completion** üéâ

**What the client does:**
- Reviews final milestone completion
- Approves final milestone
- Final payment is automatically released
- Project status changes to "Completed"
- Can rate and review the professional
- Receives project documentation

**Security & Ease:**
- ‚úÖ Final approval before final payment
- ‚úÖ All work documented with photos
- ‚úÖ Project history saved in your account
- ‚úÖ Easy rating system
- ‚úÖ Can share completed project publicly

**What happens next:**
- Professional receives final payment
- Client can use professional again in the future
- Project is saved in client's portfolio

---

