# Mercado Me - Professional Benefits & How It Works

## Overview
This document outlines the benefits of being a professional on Mercado Me and how the platform works for service providers.

---

## **Why Join Mercado Me as a Professional?**

### **üéØ Main Benefits**

1. **Access to Quality Leads**
   - Get notified about service requests in your area
   - Clients are pre-qualified and ready to hire
   - No cold calling or door-to-door marketing needed

2. **Guaranteed Payments**
   - Secure escrow system ensures you get paid
   - Payments are held safely until work is approved
   - Automatic milestone-based payments
   - No chasing clients for payment

3. **Build Your Reputation**
   - Client reviews and ratings build trust
   - Showcase your portfolio and completed projects
   - Verified professional badge increases credibility
   - Public profile helps attract new clients

4. **Streamlined Project Management**
   - All project communication in one place
   - Milestone tracking keeps projects organized
   - Real-time updates and notifications
   - Professional dashboard for all your projects

5. **Team Collaboration**
   - Invite team members to projects
   - Manage larger projects efficiently
   - Coordinate with subcontractors easily
   - Share project details with your team

6. **Material Sourcing Made Easy**
   - Search and add materials directly to quotes
   - Compare prices from major retailers
   - Accurate material cost estimation
   - Save time on quote preparation

7. **Flexible Service Options**
   - Work as a professional contractor
   - Offer consulting services
   - Or do both (hybrid professional-consultant)
   - Choose projects that match your expertise

8. **Mobile-First Platform**
   - Manage everything from your phone
   - Respond to requests on the go
   - Update project status anywhere
   - Never miss an opportunity

---

## **How It Works: Professional Journey**

### **STEP 1: Create Your Professional Profile** üë§

**What you do:**
- Sign up and select "Professional" account type
- Complete your professional profile:
  - Business name and description
  - Service categories you specialize in
  - Service area/location
  - Professional photo
  - Portfolio images (up to 10 photos/videos)
  - Bio describing your services and experience

**Key Features:**
- ‚úÖ Choose multiple service categories
- ‚úÖ Set your service area
- ‚úÖ Upload portfolio to showcase your work
- ‚úÖ Professional verification process
- ‚úÖ Profile visible to potential clients

**Benefits:**
- Your profile appears in client searches
- Clients can see your ratings and reviews
- Portfolio helps you stand out
- Verified badge builds trust

**What happens next:**
- Profile is reviewed and verified
- You start receiving service requests
- Clients can find you in search results

---

### **STEP 2: Receive Service Requests** üì®

**What you do:**
- Browse "Open Requests" section
- See service requests in your area
- Filter by:
  - Service category
  - Location/distance
  - Request type (open or consultant-needed)
  - Search keywords
- View request details:
  - Client description
  - Photos of the work area
  - Service address
  - Floor plans (if client used CubiCasa)

**Types of Requests:**
- **Open Requests**: Any professional can respond
- **Direct Requests**: Client specifically chose you
- **Consultant Requests**: Client wants professional advice first

**Benefits:**
- ‚úÖ See all relevant requests in one place
- ‚úÖ Filter to find projects that match your skills
- ‚úÖ View detailed information before responding
- ‚úÖ No need to search for clients yourself

**What happens next:**
- You review requests that interest you
- Decide which ones to quote
- Contact client via chat if you have questions

---

### **STEP 3: Create and Send Quotes** üíº

**What you do:**
- Review the service request details
- Optionally schedule a site visit (if needed)
- Create a detailed quote including:
  - Labor cost
  - Material costs (search and add from retailers)
  - Estimated timeline
  - Project milestones (break down the work)
  - Additional notes and approach
- Invite team members (if needed)
- Submit quote to client

**Quote Features:**
- ‚úÖ Material search integration (Home Depot, Lowe's)
- ‚úÖ Milestone breakdown (optional but recommended)
- ‚úÖ Team member invitations
- ‚úÖ Professional presentation
- ‚úÖ Save as draft and finish later

**Benefits:**
- ‚úÖ Professional quote presentation
- ‚úÖ Accurate material pricing
- ‚úÖ Clear project breakdown
- ‚úÖ Milestones help with payment structure
- ‚úÖ Team collaboration from the start

**What happens next:**
- Client receives your quote
- Client can ask questions via chat
- Client compares quotes from different professionals
- You get notified if client accepts your quote

---

### **STEP 4: Get Selected and Receive Payment** üí∞

**What you do:**
- Receive notification when client accepts your quote
- Client makes secure payment (held in escrow)
- Payment is confirmed and project begins
- First milestone is activated

**Payment System:**
- **Escrow Protection**: Client payment is held securely
- **Milestone Payments**: Get paid as you complete each stage
- **Automatic Transfers**: Payments sent to your Stripe account
- **90% to You**: Platform fee is only 10%
- **Weekly Processing**: Milestone payments processed weekly

**Benefits:**
- ‚úÖ Guaranteed payment (no risk of non-payment)
- ‚úÖ Get paid incrementally (not all at the end)
- ‚úÖ Automatic payment processing
- ‚úÖ Secure Stripe integration
- ‚úÖ Clear payment timeline

**What happens next:**
- Project status changes to "In Progress"
- You can start working on the first milestone
- Client is notified that work has begun

---

### **STEP 5: Execute Project with Milestones** üèóÔ∏è

**What you do:**
- Work on each milestone sequentially
- Update milestone status as you progress
- Upload photos as evidence of completed work
- Mark milestone as "Completed" when done
- Wait for client approval
- Receive payment when milestone is approved
- Move to next milestone

**Milestone System:**
- Break project into manageable stages
- Each milestone has specific scope and value
- Client must approve before payment
- Payments released incrementally
- Track progress in real-time

**Benefits:**
- ‚úÖ Organized project structure
- ‚úÖ Get paid as you work (not all at the end)
- ‚úÖ Clear expectations for each stage
- ‚úÖ Client approval ensures satisfaction
- ‚úÖ Photo evidence protects both parties

**What happens next:**
- Complete milestones one by one
- Client approves each milestone
- Payments are automatically processed
