## **Payment Details for Professionals**

### **How Payments Work:**

1. **Client Payment**
   - Client pays full amount upfront
   - Payment held in secure escrow
   - You don't receive payment yet

2. **Milestone Completion**
   - You complete a milestone
   - Upload evidence (photos)
   - Mark milestone as completed

3. **Client Approval**
   - Client reviews your work
   - Approves milestone if satisfied
   - Payment is automatically processed

4. **Automatic Transfer**
   - 90% of milestone value transferred to you
   - 10% platform fee
   - Weekly payment processing
   - Funds go to your Stripe account

5. **Final Payment**
   - Complete all milestones
   - Client approves final work
   - Receive final payment
   - Project complete

### **Payment Security:**
- ‚úÖ Stripe integration (industry standard)
- ‚úÖ Secure escrow system
- ‚úÖ Automatic payment processing
- ‚úÖ Payment history tracking
- ‚úÖ No payment disputes (client must approve)

